entry.def: If one thing is unrelated to another, there is no connection between them. You can also say that two things are unrelated .

example.ex: My line of work is entirely unrelated to politics...
example.tran: 我的职业与政治完全无关。

example.ex: Two of them died from apparently unrelated causes.
example.tran: 他们中的两个人死因明显不同。

entry.tran: 不属于同一家族的；没有亲属关系的
entry.def: If one person is unrelated to another, they are not members of the same family. You can also say that two people are unrelated .

example.ex: Jimmy is adopted and thus unrelated to Beth by blood.
example.tran: 吉米是被收养的，因此和贝丝没有血缘关系。
